11
00:00:37,526 --> 00:00:44,128
who was a naturalist, a philosopher, and a hermit who lived alone on the shores of Walden Pond in Massachusetts.

12
00:00:44,589 --> 00:00:47,191
from 1845 to 1847 and he wrote about his experiences there.

13
00:00:47,191 --> 00:00:52,916
He wrote about why he went to live there and his thoughts about life and how we

14
00:00:52,916 --> 00:00:54,117
should live it.

15
