00:27:41,927 --> 00:27:43,488
There's a lot of walking in this game,

450
00:27:43,488 --> 00:27:46,031
and we wanted to have that time there

451
00:27:46,031 --> 00:27:48,593
so that players could be reflecting

452
00:27:48,593 --> 00:27:52,015
as they were engaged in these more mundane tasks

453
00:27:52,015 --> 00:27:53,216
of Thoreau's life.

454
00:27:56,540 --> 00:27:57,882
Fascinating talk, thank you.

